<% layout('layouts/infoBoilerplate') -%>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 pt-20 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')]">
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
                <i class="fas fa-question-circle text-[#fe424d] mr-3"></i> Frequently Asked Questions
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Find answers to the most common questions from our guests
                and hosts.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">

            <div class="lg:w-1/4 hidden lg:block">
                <div
                    class="sticky top-28 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-list text-[#fe424d]"></i> Categories
                    </h3>
                    <nav class="sticky-nav flex flex-col space-y-1">
                        <a href="#booking"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Booking
                            & Payments</a>
                        <a href="#cancellations"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Cancellations</a>
                        <a href="#hosting"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Hosting
                            Basics</a>
                        <a href="#safety"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Trust
                            & Safety</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="lg:w-3/4 prose-content bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] border border-gray-100">

                <div id="booking">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Booking & Payments</h2>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3 class="mt-0">When am I charged for a reservation?</h3>
                        <p>Your payment method is charged as soon as your reservation request is accepted by the host.
                            If you choose an Instant Book property, you are charged immediately upon booking.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3>What payment methods are accepted?</h3>
                        <p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover), PayPal, and
                            Apple Pay/Google Pay in supported regions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="cancellations">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-calendar-times"></i> Cancellations</h2>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3 class="mt-0">How do I cancel my reservation?</h3>
                        <p>To cancel, go to your 'Trips' page, select the reservation you wish to cancel, and click
                            'Cancel Reservation'. You will be shown your refund amount before you confirm.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3>What happens if the host cancels my booking?</h3>
                        <p>If a host cancels, you will receive a full and immediate refund. We will also help you find a
                            similar accommodation nearby for your dates.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="hosting">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Hosting Basics</h2>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3 class="mt-0">How much does it cost to list my space?</h3>
                        <p>Listing your property is completely free! We only charge a small host service fee (typically
                            3%) when a reservation is confirmed, which helps cover the cost of processing payments.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3>Do I need to be present for check-in?</h3>
                        <p>No. Many hosts use lockboxes, smart locks, or keypads to allow guests to check themselves in
                            securely.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="safety">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Trust & Safety</h2>

                    <div class="mb-8">
                        <h3 class="mt-0">Are the properties verified?</h3>
                        <p>Yes, all new hosts go through an identity verification process, and properties are monitored
                            through guest reviews and spot checks.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>